room_title: Escape room "The Fallout Shelter" by Escape SBC in Shreveport
room_description: The crazy old lady next door has a strange obsession with the apocalypse. You've seen her going in and out of some sort of bunker in her backyard. One day you and your friends decide to sneak over. Suddenly, that ONE FRIEND (you know who you are!) decides to push that big button on the wall, "just to see what it does!". Oops... bad idea! Will you find the code to stop the locks or will you be trapped in this room for the next 25 years?
